936
01:05:36,788 --> 01:05:39,499
Malaki na ang ating Kamahalan.

937
01:05:40,541 --> 01:05:42,210
-Uy, natalo namin 'yan.
-Naku.

938
01:05:42,293 --> 01:05:43,419
